    This abstract class creates the Simpplle Type Table Data Model, a type of Abstract Table Model. Table models are used throughout the simple GUI and will be subclassed often.

      • processSelected

        private void processSelected(boolean selected,
                   int row)
        If a process is selected from a non base column it is added to either the adjacent processes list or invasive species simplle type list (for MSU). If a process is selected from a base column, it adds the process to simpplle type arraylist If process is not selected and is a not a base column, will remove from adjacent processes of invasive species simpplle types list (for MSU)
        Parameters:
        selected - true if user selected a process
        row - the row where process is found
